item.description:
Lets finally meet up. My name is Chrissy, some of you know me, most of you don't. I will be one of the event organizers to try to get you guys/gals and dogs out for some exercise =).

Sunday looks SUNNY and not super cold so lets get the dogs out finally. I chose 11am cuz it may seem a bit warmer out with the sun shining.

We will meet at the usual spot when Diana was the organizer, the main gate at Bare Cove Park.
